11. // CSS grid
div and inline block creates problems with space 
also grid solves that .. 
grid.html
display: grid
grid-template-columns: 100px ; // 1 column 
grid-template-columns: 100px 200px ; // 2 column 
grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr ; // 2 column with second block
grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr ; // 2 column with equal whole block
2fr means twice 1 fr from another fr

dynamic grid is not possible 

rigid layout

